### Reg-Tech API — Tax Authority Endpoints
### Login as TA user first using auth.http

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@token = <paste-ta-jwt-here>

### ─── Browse All Submissions ───
GET {{baseUrl}}/ta/submissions?page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ─── Filter by Status ───
GET {{baseUrl}}/ta/submissions?status=VALIDATED&jurisdiction=IE&page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ─── Filter by FI ───
GET {{baseUrl}}/ta/submissions?organizationId=00000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000004&page=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ─── Get Submission Detail ───
GET {{baseUrl}}/ta/submissions/00000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000101
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ─── Validation Dashboard ───
GET {{baseUrl}}/ta/validation/dashboard?jurisdiction=IE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ─── Approve Submission ───
POST {{baseUrl}}/ta/submissions/00000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000101/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "comments": "All validation checks passed. Approved for transmission to Germany."
}

###

### ─── Reject Submission ───
POST {{baseUrl}}/ta/submissions/00000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000102/reject
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "comments": "Multiple TIN format errors. Please correct and resubmit."
}

###

### ─── Approve FI Enrolment ───
POST {{baseUrl}}/ta/enrolments/00000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000009/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "comments": "Documentation verified. GIIN confirmed."
}

###

### ─── Trigger Transmission ───
POST {{baseUrl}}/ta/submissions/00000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000101/transmit
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "destination": "DE"
}
